---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Services – Titanumy.art">
  <section class="section">
    <h1>Services</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      One small site for your business, one giant leap for your online presence.
      Everything is built with speed, clarity, and security in mind.
    </p>

    <div class="services-grid">
      <article class="service">
        <h2>Single-Page Launch Site</h2>
        <p>
          Perfect for painters, consultants, and local businesses. A focused one-page
          site with your story, services, portfolio, and contact.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Custom design with Titanumy cosmic style</li>
          <li>Mobile-first, ultra-fast static site</li>
          <li>Basic SEO + Google indexing setup</li>
          <li>Contact form wired to your email</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="service">
        <h2>Business Website</h2>
        <p>
          Multi-section site for serious businesses that need more content: services,
          team, projects, FAQs, and more.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Extra pages: services, about, blog, etc.</li>
          <li>SEO-ready structure and metadata</li>
          <li>Performance & accessibility checks</li>
          <li>Analytics hookup on request</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="service">
        <h2>Care & Security</h2>
        <p>
          Ongoing support so your site doesn’t drift in space. Light maintenance and
          security checks on a predictable schedule.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Small content updates per month</li>
          <li>Security headers & TLS sanity checks</li>
          <li>Uptime + basic monitoring configuration</li>
          <li>Occasional performance tune-ups</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .section {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    text-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.8);
  }

  .lead {
    color: #cbd5f5;
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    max-width: 40rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1.3rem;
  }

  .service {
    padding: 1.3rem 1.2rem 1.1rem;
    border-radius: 1.1rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.4);
    background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.95), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9));
  }

  .service h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .service p {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: #d1d5db;
  }

  .service ul {
    margin: 0.6rem 0 0;
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #9ca3af;
  }

  .service li + li {
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
    }
  }
</style>
